             was indicted for <rs id="t17901027-70-off376" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17901027-70-off376" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17901027-70-off376" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17901027-70-cd377" type="crimeDate">18th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17901027-70-off376 t17901027-70-cd377"></join> last, one wooden box, value 6 d. 10 lb. weight of black tea, value 30 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17901027-70-victim793" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Hurley
                        <interp inst="t17901027-70-victim793" type="surname" value="Hurley"></interp>
